cross: Paphiopedilum Stoned Susan x Paphiopedilum sanderianum

measurements.description: Eight well-arranged and spaced flowers on two 37-cm inflorescences; sepals ovate, green striped mahogany, suffuse mahogany basally; petals nodding, twisted, green, spotted and striped mahogany, hirsute edges spotted brown; pouch chartreuse, overlaid cordovan; staminode chartreuse, suffused mahogany; substance firm; texture matte.
